# e2e/_storage/ — Playwright storageState files (gitignored)
#
# This directory persists across runs but its contents (*.json) are
# gitignored per .gitignore Wave 4A entry. The .gitkeep marker keeps
# the directory itself in version control so test setup can write
# storageState files here without needing to mkdir.
#
# Z.6 — hybrid storageState pattern:
#   - operator.json — shared logged-in state for happy-path tests
#     (J-2 Lab solve, J-3 portfolio CRUD)
#   - Negative-path tests fresh-login per test (no shared state)
